[b]Purpose:[/b]To Make A Server Status Checker In PHP

[b]Step 1:[/b]Go To Your WebSite and Make A New Page Called StatucCheck.PHP and add this code you can change the backgrounds and other details if you wish.
[code]<? 
$ip = "youriphere"; 
$port = "yourporthere"; 
